-- Tonic International Subscriber to Make Mandatory Buyout Offer for Company
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-05T15:11:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/tonic-international-subscriber-to-make-mandatory-buyout-offer-for-company.html
Tonic Industries Holdings Ltd . said
in a Hong Kong stock-exchange filing today that the purchasers
of new shares in the company will own a 79.2 percent stake, and
so will make a buyout offer for all remaining stock at 10.635
Hong Kong cents per share.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  